{"action":"edit","edits":[{"new_lines":["## JSON Output Format

### Standard output (without `--extract-unknowns`)

```json
[
  {
    "image_path": "recognize_data/event_photos/group_shot.jpg",
    "faces": [
      {
        "bbox": [120, 80, 280, 260],
        "name": "Alice",
        "confidence": 0.8234
      },
      {
        "bbox": [340, 90, 500, 270],
        "name": "unknown",
        "confidence": 0.0
      }
    ]
  }
]
```

### With `--extract-unknowns` enabled

```json
[
  {
    "image_path": "recognize_data/event_photos/group_shot.jpg",
    "faces": [
      {
        "bbox": [120, 80, 280, 260],
        "name": "Alice",
        "confidence": 0.8234
      },
      {
        "bbox": [340, 90, 500, 270],
        "name": "unknown_A01",
        "confidence": 0.0,
        "unknown_id": "A01",
        "pose_yaw": 5.2
      }
    ]
  }
]
```

- `image_path`: Relative path to the processed image.
- `faces`: Array of detected faces.
  - `bbox`: Bounding box `[x1, y1, x2, y2]` in pixel coordinates.
  - `name`: Matched person name, `"unknown"`, or `"unknown_{ID}"` when extraction is enabled.
  - `confidence`: Cosine similarity score (0.0 for unknown).
  - `unknown_id`: Persistent ID assigned to this unknown person (e.g., `A01`, `B03`). Only present when `--extract-unknowns` is enabled.
  - `pose_yaw`: Estimated face yaw in degrees. Only present for extracted unknowns."],"old_lines":["## JSON Output Format

```json
[
  {
    "image_path": "recognize_data/event_photos/group_shot.jpg",
    "faces": [
      {
        "bbox": [120, 80, 280, 260],
        "name": "Alice",
        "confidence": 0.8234
      },
      {
        "bbox": [340, 90, 500, 270],
        "name": "unknown",
        "confidence": 0.0
      }
    ]
  }
]
```

- `image_path`: Relative path to the processed image.
- `faces`: Array of detected faces.
  - `bbox`: Bounding box `[x1, y1, x2, y2]` in pixel coordinates.
  - `name`: Matched person name or `"unknown"`.
  - `confidence`: Cosine similarity score (0.0 for unknown)."]}],"path":"README.md"}

